WEBVTT

00:00.553 --> 00:02.454
<i>Previously on</i>
<i>The Borgias...</i>

00:02.522 --> 00:05.390
<i>They settled</i>
<i>like crows around me -</i>

00:05.458 --> 00:08.125
<i>praying for my death.</i>

00:08.194 --> 00:10.529
Cardinal Orsini,
Cardinal De Luca.

00:10.630 --> 00:12.432
I came as soon as I heard.

00:12.499 --> 00:15.801
<i>My father lives. You failed.</i>

00:15.869 --> 00:17.369
Where are these
allies, Cesare?

00:17.471 --> 00:18.604
Who are our friends?

00:18.672 --> 00:20.339
<i>Without him,</i>
<i>what becomes of us?</i>

00:20.406 --> 00:21.607
<i>You should go.</i>
<i>It's not safe here.</i>

00:21.674 --> 00:23.208
<i>I'm to be your husband.</i>

00:23.276 --> 00:24.342
<i>Yes, but you're not yet.</i>

00:24.443 --> 00:25.844
I will send for you.

00:25.911 --> 00:27.679
What is this?
This is your freedom.

00:27.747 --> 00:30.249
Don't forget who put
it in your hands.

00:30.317 --> 00:32.218
Guards!

00:32.286 --> 00:33.820
Did you do this?
No.

00:33.888 --> 00:35.288
All this has done
is move things along

00:35.356 --> 00:37.257
a little faster than
we'd anticipated.

00:37.324 --> 00:38.658
Now I require
your assistance.

00:38.726 --> 00:40.360
And if I refuse?

00:40.428 --> 00:44.231
<i>Your cousin Catherina will</i>
<i>not be denied this chance.</i>

00:44.299 --> 00:46.566
<i>He will die.</i>
<i>As will they all die.</i>

00:47.869 --> 00:49.503
All is well here?
No.

00:49.571 --> 00:51.505
There is a plot to
kill your family.

00:51.573 --> 00:52.740
<i>When?</i>

00:52.808 --> 00:54.142
<i>Tonight. Now.</i>

00:59.315 --> 01:01.617
<i>All the snakes</i>
<i>in Rome have slid forth.</i>

01:01.685 --> 01:05.588
Who is to protect
this family if not you?

01:05.656 --> 01:07.290
<i>Ascanio betrayed us.</i>

01:07.358 --> 01:09.192
<i>Then we will</i>
<i>have to find another way.</i>

01:09.260 --> 01:10.560
The cardinals?

01:10.628 --> 01:12.161
<i>No, their families.</i>

01:12.229 --> 01:14.398
<i>Orsini. Vitelli.</i>
<i>Baglioni.</i>

01:14.466 --> 01:15.666
<i>They hate each other.</i>

01:15.733 --> 01:18.469
They hate
the Borgias more.

01:18.537 --> 01:19.770
<i>Open your eyes.</i>

01:19.872 --> 01:21.139
We're not safe.

01:21.206 --> 01:23.041
We are at war.

01:25.244 --> 01:28.118
[♪]

01:28.119 --> 01:32.119
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Borgias 3x02 ♪ </font>
<font color=#00FFFF>The Purge</font>
