01:32.144 --> 01:37.143
== sync, corrected by <font color=#00FF00>elderman</font> ==

01:37.144 --> 02:55.950
[♪]

02:59.447 --> 03:01.649
Della Rovere's escape

03:01.750 --> 03:05.687
was orchestrated
by whom?

03:05.754 --> 03:08.657
<i>Of that,</i>
<i>I must plead ignorance.</i>

03:12.429 --> 03:16.198
We are in a snake pit,

03:16.266 --> 03:21.036
surrounded by venom
and smiling vipers,

03:21.104 --> 03:25.008
and our son
pleads ignorance?

03:26.745 --> 03:29.581
Maybe it was you, hm?

03:29.682 --> 03:31.216
Ow.

03:35.354 --> 03:37.756
Let me.

03:40.993 --> 03:45.663
Maybe you helped him to
live to see another day.

03:47.299 --> 03:50.034
The day perhaps when
your beloved father

03:50.102 --> 03:52.237
breathes
his last.

03:52.304 --> 03:53.771
If you believe that,
Father,

03:53.839 --> 03:57.408
then you have lost
all faith in me.

03:57.476 --> 04:02.647
We have lost faith in
everyone, everything,

04:02.715 --> 04:06.919
even the hand
that guides us.

04:06.987 --> 04:09.421
Surely not in
your own family?

04:09.489 --> 04:12.758
Our family.

04:12.826 --> 04:15.862
That...

04:15.930 --> 04:18.865
bosom of trust
and tranquillity.

04:21.970 --> 04:24.038
No.

04:24.106 --> 04:29.277
We feel safe in
the arms of our family.

04:29.345 --> 04:32.981
But as for that
nest of vipers -

04:33.049 --> 04:34.883
called the College
of Cardinals -

04:34.951 --> 04:36.418
we shall cleanse them.

04:36.519 --> 04:38.687
Purge it.

04:38.755 --> 04:43.158
As we ourselves
have been purged.

04:50.365 --> 04:54.134
So, Brother,
who called us here?

04:54.202 --> 04:56.236
This letter.

04:56.337 --> 04:58.438
Unsigned.

04:58.506 --> 05:01.174
It promised sport against
the Borgia family.

05:01.242 --> 05:03.243
And what if a Borgia
wrote it?

05:03.311 --> 05:05.679
Too clever surely -
even for them.

05:05.746 --> 05:09.617
Can you think of a better way
to draw out their enemies?

